<subSubSection id="34B965357C44FF8F5D96FB62FE8788A4" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="7C1C36BE7C44FF8F5D96FB62FBA08978" blockId="14.[151,1437,1050,2011]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">
Comments. 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5C1CFB63FE228BE0" box="[285,493,1158,1182]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5C1CFB63FE228BE0" box="[285,493,1158,1182]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Bactericera solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5FB8FB62FC428BE0" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[697,909,1158,1182]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5E4BFB62FC4B8BE0" box="[842,900,1158,1182]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
from leaf roll galls on an unidentified 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F583BFB62FA538BE0" box="[1338,1436,1158,1182]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F583BFB62FA538BE0" box="[1338,1436,1158,1182]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Solanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species collected in RJ: Serra dos Orgãos. In addition to the description of the gall, he mentioned different larval instars and a single adult specimen with one developed forewing which was about to emerge from the larval skin. Based on the forewing venation 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5FBBFB16FC408A74" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[698,911,1266,1290]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5E4CFB16FC488A74" box="[845,903,1266,1290]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
assigned the species to the triozids suggesting it may represent a new genus. In the larvae he observed a thickened base of the antennal flagellum and concluded that the species is related to 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5F82FAD8FCC88A2D" box="[643,775,1340,1363]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5F82FAD8FCC88A2D" box="[643,775,1340,1363]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Bactericera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. With this evidence he described the species provisionally in 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5DE5FABBFEA78A08" box="[228,360,1375,1398]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5DE5FABBFEA78A08" box="[228,360,1375,1398]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Bactericera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Up to date the species has not been found again and no additional information was published. Apart from being listed in catalogues 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5F7CFA60FD2C8AE5" box="[637,739,1411,1435]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5F7CFA60FD2C8AE5" box="[637,739,1411,1435]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was cited by 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5E86FA66FB0C8AE4" author="Hodkinson, I. D. &amp; White, I. M." box="[903,1219,1410,1434]" firstAuthor="Hodkinson" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Natural History" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="491 - 523" part="15" refId="ref12608" refString="Hodkinson, I. D. &amp; White, I. M. (1981) The Neotropical Psylloidea (Homoptera: Insecta): an annotated checklist. Journal of Natural History, 15, 491 - 523." title="The Neotropical Psylloidea (Homoptera: Insecta): an annotated checklist" type="journal article" year="1981">
Hodkinson &amp; White (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5980FA66FB748AE4" box="[1153,1211,1410,1434]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1981.0">1981</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F59FEFA66FE4E8AC0" author="Burckhardt, D. &amp; Lauterer, P." firstAuthor="Burckhardt" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Natural History" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="99 - 153" part="31" refId="ref10097" refString="Burckhardt, D. &amp; Lauterer, P. (1997) A taxonomic reassessment of the triozid genus Bactericera (Hemiptera: Psylloidea). Journal of Natural History, 31, 99 - 153." title="A taxonomic reassessment of the triozid genus Bactericera (Hemiptera: Psylloidea)" type="journal article" year="1997">
Burckhardt &amp; Lauterer (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5C3AFA42FEB78AC0" box="[315,376,1446,1470]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1997.0">1997</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. The former listed 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5F6FFA4CFD178AC0" box="[622,728,1446,1471]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5F6FFA4CFD178AC0" box="[622,728,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
under 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5E32FA43FCB68AC0" box="[819,889,1447,1470]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Trioza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5E32FA43FCB68AC0" box="[819,889,1447,1470]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Trioza</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
arguing that 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5923FA42FB3A8AC0" author="Crawford, D. L." box="[1058,1269,1446,1470]" firstAuthor="Crawford's" journalOrPublisher="Broteria: Serie zoologica" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="56 - 74" part="22" refId="ref11341" refString="Crawford, D. L. (1925) Psyllidae of South America. Broteria: Serie zoologica, 22, 56 - 74." title="Psyllidae of South America" type="journal article" year="1925">
Crawford's (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F59B2FA42FB228AC0" box="[1203,1261,1446,1470]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1925.0">1925</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
synonymy of 
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5DC6FA2FFEE88A9D" box="[199,295,1483,1507]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Aconoza</emphasis>
, erected by 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5CBCFA2EFD598A9C" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[445,662,1482,1506]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5F55FA2EFD418A9C" box="[596,654,1482,1506]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
as subgenus of 
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5E5DFA28FC1B8A9D" box="[860,980,1484,1507]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Batericera</emphasis>
for 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F590DFA28FB968A9D" box="[1036,1113,1483,1507]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Trioza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ulei">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F590DFA28FB968A9D" box="[1036,1113,1483,1507]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. ulei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, with 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F59A8FA28FB208A9D" box="[1193,1263,1484,1507]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Trioza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F59A8FA28FB208A9D" box="[1193,1263,1484,1507]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Trioza</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, automatically applies also to 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5C6FFA14FE1E8978" box="[366,465,1518,1543]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5C6FFA14FE1E8978" box="[366,465,1518,1543]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This view was followed by 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5E17FA0AFBA38978" author="Burckhardt, D. &amp; Lauterer, P." box="[790,1132,1518,1542]" firstAuthor="Burckhardt" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Natural History" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="99 - 153" part="31" refId="ref10097" refString="Burckhardt, D. &amp; Lauterer, P. (1997) A taxonomic reassessment of the triozid genus Bactericera (Hemiptera: Psylloidea). Journal of Natural History, 31, 99 - 153." title="A taxonomic reassessment of the triozid genus Bactericera (Hemiptera: Psylloidea)" type="journal article" year="1997">
Burckhardt &amp; Lauterer (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5927FA0AFBAC8978" box="[1062,1123,1518,1542]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1997.0">1997</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7C1C36BE7C44FF8F5D96F9F6FC6289C4" blockId="14.[151,1437,1050,2011]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">
During recent field work in SC we found adults and larvae associated with leaf roll galls on 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F59ACF9F7FA5A8955" box="[1197,1429,1555,1579]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ramulosum">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F59ACF9F7FA5A8955" box="[1197,1429,1555,1579]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Solanum ramulosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The galls, adults and larvae fit 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5F33F9D2FCD68930" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[562,793,1590,1614]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen's" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen's (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5FD7F9D2FCDF8930" box="[726,784,1590,1614]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
decription, though the forewing vein Rs seems slightly longer in our specimens. Similar galls were also found in PR on 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5EE5F9BFFB89890D" box="[996,1094,1627,1651]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5EE5F9BFFB89890D" box="[996,1094,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Solanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. and 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F59B7F9BFFA53890D" box="[1206,1436,1627,1651]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Acnistus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="breviflorus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F59B7F9BFFA53890D" box="[1206,1436,1627,1651]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Acnistus breviflorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5DCEF99AFE9B89E8" box="[207,340,1662,1686]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Solanaceae</taxonomicName>
). Larvae were present in both samples, adults, however, only in the former. Again the adult and larval morphology corresponds to 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5F49F946FCE389C4" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[584,812,1698,1722]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen's" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen's (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5FEBF946FCEB89C4" box="[746,804,1698,1722]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
decription.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7C1C36BE7C44FF8F5D96F923FE8788A4" blockId="14.[151,1437,1050,2011]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">
A detailed examination of our material showed that the two samples from 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5EE0F922FB8C89A0" box="[993,1091,1734,1758]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5EE0F922FB8C89A0" box="[993,1091,1734,1758]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Solanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represent two different triozid species, and that the sample from 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5F4CF90FFD63887D" box="[589,684,1771,1795]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Acnistus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5F4CF90FFD63887D" box="[589,684,1771,1795]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Acnistus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represents a third. 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5E89F90EFBA1887C" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[904,1134,1770,1794]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen's" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen's (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F592DF90EFBA9887C" box="[1068,1126,1770,1794]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
description is not detailed enough to indicate which if any of our three species is conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5EEAF8F4FB808858" box="[1003,1103,1806,1831]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5EEAF8F4FB808858" box="[1003,1103,1806,1831]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectingCountry id="04B4762E7C44FF8F595CF8EBFBB38859" box="[1117,1148,1807,1831]" name="American Samoa" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">As</collectingCountry>
apart from the herbarium sheet the 
<typeStatus id="A318881C7C44FF8F5C33F8D7FEAD8835" box="[306,354,1843,1867]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">type</typeStatus>
material seems to be lost its identity cannot be elucidated at present. More field work may help to solve the problem. On the other hand 
<bibRefCitation id="18324B4F7C44FF8F5F9EF8B2FC498810" author="Rubsaamen, E. H." box="[671,902,1878,1902]" firstAuthor="Rubsaamen's" journalOrPublisher="Marcellia" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" pagination="15 - 79" part="7" refId="ref15040" refString="Rubsaamen, E. H. (1908) Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru. Marcellia, 7, 15 - 79." title="Beitrage zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Zoocecidien. 3. Beitrag: Gallen aus Brasilien und Peru" type="journal article" year="1908">
Rübsaamen's (
<number id="CA6B24997C44FF8F5E45F8B2FCB18810" box="[836,894,1878,1902]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" value="1908.0">1908</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
indications suggest that our recently collected triozids on 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5C46F89EFE0A88EC" box="[327,453,1914,1938]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Solanaceae</taxonomicName>
are congeneric with 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5FB4F898FCD488ED" box="[693,795,1915,1939]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5FB4F898FCD488ED" box="[693,795,1915,1939]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">B. solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and with 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5E8CF898FB7388EC" authority="Crawford" authorityName="Crawford" box="[909,1212,1914,1939]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Trioza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculata">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5E8CF898FB8A88ED" box="[909,1093,1915,1939]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Trioza maculata</emphasis>
Crawford
</taxonomicName>
, the 
<typeStatus id="A318881C7C44FF8F59F2F89FFAEC88ED" box="[1267,1315,1915,1939]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5DC6F844FEF488C9" box="[199,315,1952,1975]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Leuronota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5DC6F844FEF488C9" box="[199,315,1952,1975]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Leuronota</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. For this reason we transfer here 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5FAEF87BFCB088C8" box="[687,895,1950,1974]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Bactericera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5FAEF87BFCB088C8" box="[687,895,1950,1974]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Bactericera solani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F5EA3F844FBD988C9" box="[930,1046,1952,1975]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Leuronota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5EA3F844FBD988C9" box="[930,1046,1952,1975]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Leuronota</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as 
<taxonomicName id="BBA34D3D7C44FF8F593BF844FA5788C8" authority="Rubsaamen" authorityName="Rubsaamen" box="[1082,1432,1950,1975]" class="Insecta" family="Triozidae" genus="Leuronota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solani" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F593BF844FB3788C8" box="[1082,1272,1950,1975]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">Leuronota solani</emphasis>
(Rübsaamen)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="55E457D77C44FF8F5DC6F827FE8788A4" box="[199,328,1987,2011]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="4ED7EAAC7C44FF8F5DC6F827FE8788A4" bold="true" box="[199,328,1987,2011]" pageId="14" pageNumber="40">comb. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
